<L>__{exterior forests day}
<A>__{a black horse runs, hooves pounding the ground. thunder is heard. the horse slows and stops... it is brom's horse, with brom aboard. brom looks skyward. the storm harshens, roaring through the trees. distant hoofbeats can be heard. pounding. brom takes his rifle off his shoulder. the hoofbeats grow louder and pass, far away. brom turns in the saddle and whistles. he kicks his horse and rides.}
